# Code Owners for OmniOps
#
# This file defines code ownership for automatic PR review assignments.
# When a PR touches these files/directories, the specified owners are
# automatically requested for review.
#
# Format: <file-pattern> <owner1> <owner2> ...
# Use @username for individuals or @org/team for teams

